or at the Army Headquarters in Abuja. <img class="alignnone  wp-image-10394 lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="https://mlpthjcvvzze.i.optimole.com/l57LFPo.2zvi~5f0f9/w:auto/h:auto/q:90/https://i0.wp.com/ebitu.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Screenshot-2021-05-05-at-1.47.18-AM.png?resize=84,26&amp;ssl=1" alt="EBITU | #EbituBlog" width="84" height="26" data-recalc-dims="1"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-10394 lazyload jetpack-lazy-image" src="https://i1.wp.com/mlpthjcvvzze.i.optimole.com/l57LFPo.2zvi~5f0f9/w:auto/h:auto/q:90/https://i0.wp.com/ebitu.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Screenshot-2021-05-05-at-1.47.18-AM.png?resize=84%2C26&#038;ssl=1" alt="EBITU | #EbituBlog" width="84" height="26" data-recalc-dims="1" data-lazy-src="https://i1.wp.com/mlpthjcvvzze.i.optimole.com/l57LFPo.2zvi~5f0f9/w:auto/h:auto/q:90/https://i0.wp.com/ebitu.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Screenshot-2021-05-05-at-1.47.18-AM.png?resize=84%2C26&amp;is-pending-load=1#038;ssl=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7"><noscript><img class="alignnone  wp-image-10394 lazyload" src="https://i1.wp.com/mlpthjcvvzze.i.optimole.com/l57LFPo.2zvi~5f0f9/w:auto/h:auto/q:90/https://i0.wp.com/ebitu.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Screenshot-2021-05-05-at-1.47.18-AM.png?resize=84%2C26&#038;ssl=1" alt="EBITU | #EbituBlog" width="84" height="26" data-recalc-dims="1" data-recalc-dims="1"> The post JUST IN: Nigerian Army General Hassan Ahmed assassinated in Abuja, wife abducted appeared first on E B I T U™.